          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SILI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " the elastic scattered deuteron were detected",
                "by a 2 mm thick Si(Li) counter after being analyzed in",
                "a high-resolution magnetic spectrograph."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MAGSP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A 0.6 mm thick surface barrier counter was",
                "placed at a fixed angle in the spectrograph target",
                "chamber and served as a monitor by recording",
                "elastically scattered deuterons."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The correction because of the finite solid angle of the",
                "spectrograph was shown to be less than 0.5%."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The targets were made by evaporation of",
                " 142,144,146,148,150Nd(2)O(3) onto thin carbon",
                "backings. The target thicknesses were approximately",
                " 150 mug/cm**2. The isotope enrichments in the Nd",
                "targets were 85% for the Nd-148 and more than 95% for",
                "the others."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COMP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ".Optical model analysis."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-S",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": 2.0,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                ".Statistical error was kept below 2% at all",
                "angles."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                ".From the uncertainty in setting the angle",
                "and minor variations in the solid angle of the",
                "spectrograph of variations in the beam spot position,",
                "the cross sections should be accurate within 4%."
              ]
            }
